" You can close your eyes to the things you don't want to see, But you can't close your heart to the things you don't want to feel"
Finally,Started the incredible  marvellous musical journey with a splendid lively Pakistan! Neither you can close your eyes to the exceptional and extraordinary  beauty of Pakistan nor you can close your heart from feeling what a melodious, peaceful,beautiful, glorious, brave ,  lovely and amazing nation Pakistan is, BUT you must close your eyes from shitty filthy media if you want to see the beauty of beautiful Pakistan and feel what Pakistan is........
Huge love for Pakistan, Pity on Pakistan's foes 
My blessings with Pakistan, My condolence with those
Huge love from USA
Long Live Pakistan........
